<dl id="n08032g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08032g">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08032g"> 32(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Buck frightened out of / his life, crying</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>Home on Leave</b> He thought the deceased was hot-tempered in striking Private Buckley. He saw <mark>Buckley</mark> crying, and he appeared to be <mark>frightened out of his life</mark>. <small> <a name="FJ29dec23" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ29dec23"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (29 December 1923) 5/2</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
